data.name: 0000 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: They say that "great men thirst greater," so what can you expect from common men?

data.name: 0001 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: What are you talking about?

data.name: 0002 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: No, it's nothing. I'm just talking to myself.

data.name: 0003 (367.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Your instructions?

data.name: 0004 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I'm not going to tell you to do anything in particular.

data.name: 0005 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: As long as you're friendly with all the members of the computer club, that should do the trick.

data.name: 0006 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I'm sorry to say, but I don't think the computer club has high female resistance.

data.name: 0007 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: If I soften their attitude, it should be easier to get them to talk.

data.name: 0008 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Alright, shall we go?

data.name: 0011 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hiya~

data.name: 0012 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Y-You guys again?!

data.name: 0013 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: No matter how many times you come, we have nothing more to tell you!

data.name: 0014 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Now! Asahina, Nagato!

data.name: 0015 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: O-Okay.

data.name: 0016 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Um, uhh… we've come to visit you... to support you after all your hard work during this summer camp~

data.name: 0017 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: … Eh?

data.name: 0019 (367.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Have some tea.

data.name: 0020 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Asahina is awkward, and Nagato is completely monotone.

data.name: 0021 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: However, for the time being it seems their appeal is working.

data.name: 0022 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Behold, the computer club members' cheeks are dyed red. They can't stop fidgeting…

data.name: 0023 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: You've become hopelessly stricken by their appeal, haven't you?

data.name: 0025 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Um, well, I came to bring you tea.

data.name: 0026 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I know it's not much, but…

data.name: 0027 (367.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: There is also a pot. I will use the outlet.

data.name: 0028 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Rejoice, Comp Club!

data.name: 0029 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It's not every day that you get ambushed by the Nagato-Asahina tag team.

data.name: 0030 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It's a dream combination, after all.

data.name: 0031 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: O-Oh of course, I'm sorry… for not being more considerate.

data.name: 0032 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: No, it's fine. Our leader is always causing you trouble, so consider this an apology.

data.name: 0033 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: We don't have any girls in our club,

data.name: 0034 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: so this is certainly a fresh experience…

data.name: 0035 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The president's spellbound gaze was directed at Nagato and Asahina.

data.name: 0038 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nagato was pulling her usual poker face.

data.name: 0041 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Whenever Asahina's eyes met the president's, she lowered her face in embarrassment.

data.name: 0042 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …We once extorted a computer from them in one of Haruhi's schemes.

data.name: 0043 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: You'd expect the president to be recalling the terrible things he's been put through.

data.name: 0045 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Though, when you actually look at him…

data.name: 0046 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: I wish either one of those two would join our club…

data.name: 0047 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He mumbled something along those lines.

data.name: 0050 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Without a doubt, my choice is Asahina.

data.name: 0051 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: As long as I have a cup of her tea, I feel like I could endure any carnage.

data.name: 0052 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: On that front, it seems the computer club members are of the same opinion.

data.name: 0053 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Their twinkling eyes have been stealing glances at Asahina for a while now.

data.name: 0054 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Granted, it may only be because of the maid outfit.

data.name: 0057 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Well, between the two of them it would have to be Nagato.

data.name: 0058 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Asahina definitely heals you, but she won't be the solution to the situation.

data.name: 0059 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But with Nagato, she'll handle it quickly and calmly like always.

data.name: 0062 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Would you also like some tea, Kyon?

data.name: 0063 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Before I knew it, Asahina had somehow become completely absorbed in serving tea.

data.name: 0064 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I wonder if it's a personality thing, or more like some kind of work-related sickness?

data.name: 0065 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Day-dreaming about such things, I sipped Asahina's tea while lazily looking around.

data.name: 0066 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: There are various documents scattered around…

data.name: 0067 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: There really are. Did you make these posters on the computers?

data.name: 0068 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Asahina pointed to a poster sitting on a desk, and a member nodded.

data.name: 0069 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: Th-This kind of thing is nothing. Anyone could do it. Easy-peasy.

data.name: 0070 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Despite that, he's looking awfully proud about himself. I'll take a look at it I guess.

data.name: 0071 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …Eh.

data.name: 0072 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: "Take care of water!" A water preservation awareness school poster, huh?

data.name: 0073 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: It was a request from the student council. Not bad, right?

data.name: 0074 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: It's amazing how such a primitive device is able to produce such a beautiful poster.

data.name: 0075 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Asahina nodded as her eyes widened in amazement.

data.name: 0076 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: However, that's not how you should show your admiration. Please be more careful.

data.name: 0077 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Though… When I look at this poster, there's something that catches my attention.

data.name: 0078 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The symbol "H20," which is to say, "water" is rendered digitally, but…

data.name: 0079 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: For some reason, I got the impression that something was off about it.

data.name: 0080 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …Ah, I get it.

data.name: 0081 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: What it should say is "H2O," but...

data.name: 0082 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The 2 was missing so it became "HO."

data.name: 0083 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Also, the "H" was stretched out too wide.

data.name: 0084 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Depending on how you looked at it, the "HO" seemed more like a "1-10."

data.name: 0085 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Should I point it out?

data.name: 0086 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Although Asahina and Nagato's entertainment did brighten the mood.

data.name: 0087 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Would pointing it out put a damper on that?

data.name: 0088 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: So then, what should I do…?

data.name: 0089 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Uhh, could borrow you for a moment?

data.name: 0090 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: …What is it?

data.name: 0091 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Yeah, I understand how you feel.

data.name: 0092 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I'm getting in the way of you having fun talking to Asahina.

data.name: 0093 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Excuse me but, about this poster…

data.name: 0094 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Isn't the "2" of this "H2O" missing here?

data.name: 0095 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: Eh!? That can't be right…

data.name: 0096 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The club member took the poster and held it right up to his face.

data.name: 0097 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: …Aaah, it really is!

data.name: 0098 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: It's drawn the same color as the background so you can't see it at all!

data.name: 0099 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Also, the letter "H" is definitely too wide.

data.name: 0100 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It looks less like an H… and more like "1-1."

data.name: 0101 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: Th-that too, now that you mention it…

data.name: 0102 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: It said "H2O?"

data.name: 0103 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I was certain it read as "1-10".

data.name: 0104 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: As is, I don't think it gets the intended message across.

data.name: 0105 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Wouldn't it be best take down the posters you've already put up?

data.name: 0106 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You should hurry and remake them. If you do it now, I'm sure no-one will notice.

data.name: 0107 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: Ugh, I guess so… Well, it'll be easy to remake anyways.

data.name: 0108 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: It's going to be hard going around and taking them all down though…

data.name: 0109 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I chose to sympathize with the club member's dejection.

data.name: 0110 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Because thanks to this, I think I've got some nice material to deceive Haruhi with.

data.name: 0113 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Ah, would you like a second helping of tea?

data.name: 0114 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: I-Is that okay? In that case, thank you very much.

data.name: 0115 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Yes, please wait just a moment.

data.name: 0116 (367.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Here.

data.name: 0117 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Hya!

data.name: 0118 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: ……Did you prepare it in advance?

data.name: 0119 (367.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Yes.

data.name: 0120 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Th, thank you very much! Okay, here's your tea.

data.name: 0121 (367.ja) CLUB_MEM_A (部員Ａ)
data.value: Thanks……Ahh, it's delicious.

data.name: 0122 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: After receiving the entertainment of Nagato and Asahina,

data.name: 0123 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The computer club was wrapped in a warm and comforting mood.

data.name: 0124 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It looks like going through the trouble of pointing out the mistake didn't ruin the mood.

data.name: 0126 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Your group, does it always have this feeling?

data.name: 0127 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What do you mean feeling?

data.name: 0128 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The club president's gaze followed the two girls as they poured the member's tea.

data.name: 0129 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: That's what happened.

data.name: 0130 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Well……I don't know about that.

data.name: 0131 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It was the usual scene of Asahina diligently brewing tea.

data.name: 0132 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nagato making tea though, I thought was a very rare sight.

data.name: 0133 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: About half the time, it has that feeling I'd say.

data.name: 0134 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: You guys have it nice don't you……It seems like fun. Our club is a mess.

data.name: 0135 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: I wouldn't complain if there was a single female member.

data.name: 0136 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: It's all because of your club leader's false accusations of sexual harassment.

data.name: 0137 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: She plundered our precious club budget to buy that computer.

data.name: 0138 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: That's why the first semester was a horrible experience……

data.name: 0139 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The club president dropped his shoulders and began mumbling and grumbling.

data.name: 0140 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Not good, if this goes on I have a feeling I'll be associated with those complaints.

data.name: 0141 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It would be best to dodge the topic and distract him with tea. I'll call out to the girls.

data.name: 0142 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Oi~, Nagato! Ask Asahina for another serving of tea.

data.name: 0143 (367.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: ……Certainly.

data.name: 0144 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Hurry!

data.name: 0146 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Th, thank you.

data.name: 0148 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What's wrong? You're staring at a computer.

data.name: 0149 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Are you perhaps interested in computers by any chance?

data.name: 0150 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: If you want, I can teach you?

data.name: 0151 (367.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: ……It's fine.

data.name: 0152 (367.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Not right now.

data.name: 0153 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: I, I see……

data.name: 0154 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Immediately after getting refused, the president slumped his shoulders.

data.name: 0155 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: ……Even if it was just flattery, you should've said "I'm really interested~" or something.

data.name: 0156 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: ……Actually, Nagato saying something like, I cant imagine it at all.

data.name: 0159 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Asahinaa!

data.name: 0160 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Please bring Mr President another serving of tea~

data.name: 0161 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Ye, Yes, I'll be right there.

data.name: 0162 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: She responded with a slightly high-pitched voice, and brought the teapot.

data.name: 0164 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: He……Here you go.

data.name: 0165 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Asahina came over right away with a very clumsy demeanor.

data.name: 0166 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: By any chance, is it because when Haruhi did that outrageous thing to the club president,

data.name: 0167 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Asahina is being reminded of that?

data.name: 0168 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Everything's okay, Asahina.

data.name: 0169 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Haruhi isn't here now, so nothing will happen.

data.name: 0170 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Tha, that's true isn't it……

data.name: 0171 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: ……Are, are you always exposed to horrible experiences like that?

data.name: 0172 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: No one would blame you if you just resigned from such a horrible group……

data.name: 0173 (367.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I'm sorry, I, there are circumstances that prevent me from doing that……

data.name: 0174 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: I, I understand……What a cruel person……

data.name: 0175 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The club president somehow thinks that Haruhi is blackmailing her with some weakness.

data.name: 0176 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I feel as though some misunderstanding took place……Well no need to correct it.

data.name: 0179 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Either way, the atmosphere in the computer lab became brighter.

data.name: 0180 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: However, I still wasn't able to get any particularly new information.

data.name: 0181 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: At any rate that's because I already came here to gather information once before.

data.name: 0182 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi already made you spill everything, so it seems there's no new info left.

data.name: 0183 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Asahina, Nagato, we had better head back soon.

data.name: 0184 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Why in the world did you guys even come here?

data.name: 0185 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Was it really just to treat us to tea?

data.name: 0186 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Unfortunately, somehow or another that seems to be the case.

data.name: 0187 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The president shrugged his shoulders with a sigh, sensing something in my response.

data.name: 0188 (367.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: I see……I guess you guys have trouble of your own.

data.name: 0189 (367.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Thank you very much.

data.name: 0190 (367.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Something doesn't add up, but for now we should go regroup with the other team.

data.name: 0191 (367.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Asahina.

data.name: 0192 (367.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Nagato.

data.name: 0193 (367.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Point it out.

data.name: 0194 (367.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Don't point it out.

data.name: 0195 (367.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Call Nagato.

data.name: 0196 (367.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Call Asahina.
